{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"34":"Clothing (Kitab Al-Libas)"}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":4030,"arabicnumber":4030,"text":"মুসাদ্দা (রহঃ) .... আবূ আওয়ানা (রাঃ) এর বর্ণনায় আছে যে, আল্লাহ কিয়ামতের দিন তাকে অসম্মানের পোশাক পরিধান করাবেন।","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Hasan"}],"reference":{"book":34,"hadith":11}}]}